            <h2>Planos</h2>
            <p>Confira alguns de nossos planos: </p>
          </div>
          <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
              <div class="col-md-5 col-lg-4">
                  <div class="item">  
                      <div class="heading">
                          <h3>Plano Simples</h3>
                      </div>
                      <p>Texto sobre o Plano.</p>
                      <div class="features">
                          <h4><span class="feature">Suporte Extra</span> : <span class="value">Sim</span></h4>
                          <h4><span class="feature">Benefícios</span> : <span class="value">Sim</span></h4>
                          <h4><span class="feature">Duração do plano</span> : <span class="value">60 dias</span></h4>
